    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Term of Medieval origin generally applied to tall cupboards with doors and shelves for storing linens, clothing, and kitchen utensils. For presses with sliding shelves behind closed doors, use "clothes presses."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000114707/Oxford English Dictionary Online (2002-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Término de origen medieval aplicado generalmente a aparadores altos con puertas y repisas para guardar lino, ropa y utensilios de cocina. Para armarios con estantes corredizos detrás de puertas cerradas, use "armario de ropa.”</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Benaming uit de middeleeuwen die meestal van toepassing is op grote wandkasten met deuren en planken om linnengoed, kleding en keukengerei in op te bergen. Gebruik 'clothes presses' voor presses met schuivende planken en dichte deuren.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
